high_descs: Hang a right and go to the wall, turn to the left to face the white table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Back up from the table.
Cut the tomato that is on the table into slices.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a left, go to the stove on the other side of the room.
Put the knife into the rightmost blue pan on the stove.
Turn around, go across the room, hang a right, go to the wall, turn left to face the white table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a left, go to the stove on the other side of the room.
Put the tomato into the blue pan that contains the knife.
Pick up the pan from the stove that contains the knife and tomato.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the pan inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing tomato and a knife inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, cross the room, then turn left to face the round white table
Pick up the knife
Continue to face the round white table
Slice the tomato that is sitting on the table
Turn left and head to the trash can, then turn left and walk to the stove across the room to your left
Place the knife in the pan that is on the right back burner of the stove
Turn around and cross the room, once past the counter take a right and head to the wall, then turn left and face the round white table
Pick up a slice of the tomato
Turn to your left and head across the room, once past the first counter on your left, turn left and walk to the stove
Place the tomato in the pan that on the right back burner, the one that contains the knife
Pick up the pan that contains the knife and the tomato slice
Turn to your right and walk to the black fridge
Open the fridge and place the pan containing the knife and tomato inside on the slotted shelf then close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a knife and tomato into a fridge

high_descs: Go to the round white table
Pick up the knife
Look at the tomato
Cut the tomato
Go to the stove
Put the knife on a pan
Go to the round white table
Pick up a tomato slice
Go to the stove
Put the tomato slice on the pan
Pick up the pan
Go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a tomato slice and a knife in the fridge
